        <h2>Instructions</h2>
        <p>
            Using ASP.NET forms or MVC build an e-commerce ordering system with the following features:
        </p>
        <ol>
            <li>Create new product, modify a product and delete a product if there are no orders associated with it</li>
            <li>Place an order, modify an order and process an order</li>
            <li>Change order status from created to processed and shipped</li>
            <li>Disable order editing once the status is either processed or shipped</li>
